                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Eula is a Cryo Physical DMG character with a claymore, which synergizes with this weapon's Physical DMG. Additionally, she can make good use of this weapon's special effect.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 48,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Razor_icon.png",
                      "name": "Razor",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Razor is an effective Physical DMG DPS character with a claymore. When Ascended, he gains additional Physical DMG, which synergizes with this weapon's sub-stats and improves his type-B DMG and Physical DMG from its special effect. Therefore, this weapon is an ideal choice for Razor among 4-star weapons. Depending on the situation, Prototype Archaic may be a better choice, but the difference is negligible.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 41,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xinyan_icon.png",
                      "name": "Xinyan",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Xinyan is generally used for quick swap or battlefield Charge Attack team comps. This weapon provides negligible benefit for Charge Attacks. At the highest Constellation rank, Whiteblind provides a higher stat boost. Therefore, this weapon is most suitable for C2-5 quick swap builds.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
